---

---

<section id="cta" class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg">
    <img 
      src="/images/cta-camping.jpg"
      alt="焚き火を囲むキャンプの夜"
      class="cta-bg-img"
    />
    <div class="cta-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container cta-content">
    <div class="cta-inner reveal">
      <span class="cta-icon">🎟️</span>
      <h2 class="cta-title">Join Us!</h2>
      <p class="cta-desc">
        大人気の「宿泊キャンプチケット」は数量限定です。<br class="pc-only">
        過去のイベントでは即完売の実績も多数ありますので、<br class="pc-only">
        お早めのチェックをおすすめします。
      </p>

      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="cta-btn-primary">
          <span class="cta-btn-icon">⛺</span>
          宿泊チケットを購入する
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:info@bikeand.camp" class="cta-btn-secondary">
          <span class="cta-btn-icon">📩</span>
          出展・ボランティアのお問い合わせ
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-note">
        <p>※ チケット販売サイトへ移動します（準備中）</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8rem 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cta-section {
      padding: 10rem 3rem;
    }
  }

  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .cta-bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .cta-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: 
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.85) 0%, rgba(15, 52, 96, 0.75) 50%, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.7) 100%);
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .cta-desc {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .pc-only {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pc-only {
      display: inline;
    }
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  .cta-btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sunset), var(--color-coral));
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .cta-btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 35px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.6);
  }

  .cta-btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .cta-btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-btn-icon {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-note p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  }
</style>
